{"tid":28102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨發難：TRUMP愚蠢台灣通話 觸怒中國危及國防","createTime":"2016-12-07T17:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T19:09:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce8b713a3947b3003b4f6492b60e565e2bcbe17","tid":28102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:39:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20161203002633-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20161203002633-260408&d=uxwN5JqRpwkDwaH%2Br6EYGnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=474e89c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20161203002633-260408</a> <br />\n美國總統當選人川普與蔡英文2日通話在美國國內激起政治波瀾。美國民主黨全國委員會發表聲明批評川普，指沒法理解川普「愚蠢的電話」威脅美國國家安全，或者是川普將個人財富置於國家安全利益之上。 <br />\n<br />\n據中評網報導，民主黨全國委員會發言人埃里克&middot;沃克發表題為「川普的愚蠢台灣電話」的聲明，全文如下：「唐納&middot;川普或者是太無能，沒法理解他的愚蠢的電話威脅我們的國家安全，或者是他故意這麼做，因為有報導說他想在台灣興建飯店中飽私囊。鑒於唐納&middot;川普沒有公布他的報稅記錄，也沒有從他的生意中脫離出來，川普似乎是將其個人財富置於國家安全利益之上。」 <br />\n<br />\n川普於美東時間2日晚間7點44分發推特說是蔡英文打電話給他，祝賀他當選之後，又於晚間8點41分發推特說：「真有意思，為什麼美國每年賣給台灣數十億美元的武器給台灣，我難道不能接（來自台灣）的恭賀電話嗎？」似在反駁民主黨的批評。"},{"pid":"ae3313b6729cd4fff19a9130faa841b1d91259e6","tid":28102,"uid":2797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:41:31.000Z","msg":"不舐共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499dab42a006aacddb82086dd456cb6f90744416","tid":28102,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"又係個種 收左外國錢搞事 既論調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如直接話佢retard 做乜撚野總統啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8308eaf68f72f863dc2256f42cc1af05911d4e6f","tid":28102,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:43:23.000Z","msg":"以爲白鴿黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758ebb624d867cc44ab221665394bb838ecb8fb0","tid":28102,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:32:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以爲白鴿黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4c246944a0df75744efc31c395cc7f6f12dac0","tid":28102,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以爲白鴿黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佔中時期口吻一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf3b20efd085089b47789773df8b1e029ec0d1e","tid":28102,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以爲白鴿黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佔中時期口吻一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係口說民主，但最怕民主( 有睇斯諾登風暴就會明 )"},{"pid":"67b38c7d61315bda05f25fcc23df31bdfc95c1e8","tid":28102,"uid":59626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:54:12.000Z","msg":"死啦玩大左 搵唔到位落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e0c4902727b0c71bfc51e51dc59f8894bf0c5b","tid":28102,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T19